@startuml Learning Phase User Interaction

actor User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "AI Knowledge Base" as AI

title Learning Phase - User Interaction with Resources

== Resource Upload (Leader) ==

User -> UI: Navigate to Learning Phase Section
User -> UI: Select "Upload Resource"
User -> UI: Choose file and enter name
UI -> API: POST /section/:sectionId/resource
API -> API: Process and store file
API -> AI: Add to knowledge base (if applicable)
API --> UI: Return success
UI --> User: Show success message

== Resource Access (Member) ==

User -> UI: Navigate to Learning Phase Section
UI -> API: GET /subteam/:subTeamId/learningphase
API --> UI: Return sections with resources
UI --> User: Display resources list
User -> UI: Click on resource
UI -> API: GET /resource/:resourceId
API --> UI: Return resource file
UI --> User: Display/download resource

== AI Chat Based on Resources ==

User -> UI: Navigate to Learning Phase Chat
User -> UI: Enter question about learning materials
UI -> API: POST /subteam/:subTeamId/learningphase/chat
API -> AI: Query knowledge base with question
AI --> API: Return AI-generated response
API --> UI: Return chat response
UI --> User: Display AI response

@enduml
